SOLLOG NFT God EL Crypto Gods Gold Portrait Series 1/7 Minting 1x10^6

Sollog is a listed artist in museums and the creator of CryptoGods.app He has the busiest Artist site on the Net Sollog.com and has the record for the highest sale in Art History the first $1 Billion Canvas

This series is the 9 Crypto Gods created by SOLLOG in a super rare 7 Mintings series exclusively for Tezos and HEN, that means there are only 63 Crypto Gods Gold Portraits in this limited edition Series of Crypto Gods

There are only 7 Of this Crypto God Gold Portrait

SOLLOG is a brilliant mathematician and he created a new formula for this series known as the 6 Fold Million Process or 1x10^6

1st Copy is 1 XTZ
2nd Copy is 10 XTZ
3rd Copy is 100 XTZ
4th Copy is 1000 XTZ
5th Copy is 10K XTZ
6th Copy is 100K XTZ
7th Copy is 1 Million XTZ

Now you know how to go from 1 XTZ to 1 Million in 6 Folds
